[{"id":"RAW_ebdbcf7f","title":"全网最详细的 Codex 入门教程，手把手教你玩转 Vibe Coding。","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMzA5NjEyMA==&mid=2647679828&idx=1&sn=6e1c0a935c70c566ee765c02a36327a6","date":"2026-02-09 01:29:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_ebdbcf7f.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"数字生命卡兹克","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":24,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_dd96812d","title":"Vibe Coding 在代码生成与协作中的实践与思考","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MDE0Mjc4MA==&mid=2651275013&idx=2&sn=d696ab8030134d5251ce180ff5dbcd31","date":"2026-02-10 06:05:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_dd96812d.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ 中文","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":36,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_4ead9a68","title":"Yelp 如何构建 “Yelp Assistant”","link":"https://blog.bytebytego.com/p/how-yelp-built-yelp-assistant","date":"2026-02-09 16:31:03","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_4ead9a68.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"ByteByteGo Newsletter","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":11,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_401505dd","title":"3 年、1 万人，快手技术团队首次系统披露 AI 研发范式升级历程","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MDE0Mjc4MA==&mid=2651274822&idx=1&sn=b4b364a2e23df2beda37e877001ea4df","date":"2026-02-09 05:31:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_401505dd.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ 中文","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":59,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_ea193e97","title":"UML 之父：Dario 大错特错，根本不懂软件工程！软件工程不会死亡！软件已经迎来第三次黄金时代！业界回应：有了 AI，SaaS 只会更加繁荣！","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODI5Njc2MA==&mid=2655936386&idx=1&sn=928acef652aef65bb6dc631b9f620116","date":"2026-02-10 04:29:00","oneSentenceSummary":"UML 之父 Grady Booch 深度驳斥“AI 终结软件工程”论，指出 AI 仅是抽象层级的又一次跃迁，开发者应从写代码转向系统思维。","summary":"本文记录了软件工程大师 Grady Booch 对 Anthropic CEO 关于“软件工程将死”言论的有力反击。Booch 认为，软件工程的核心在于复杂系统中的权衡与取舍，而非单纯的代码编写。他通过回顾软件工程与 AI 的三个黄金时代，阐明了技术演进始终伴随着抽象层级的提升。他预测未来代码将分化为“一次性自动化代码”与“长期存在的系统”，并建议开发者通过研习系统理论、生物学和神经科学，提升在规模化条件下管理复杂性的能力，从而在 AI 时代实现职业升维。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_ea193e97.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"51CTO技术栈","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":60,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_c72c00fd","title":"华为发布业界首个扩散语言模型 Agent，部分场景提速 8 倍！","link":"https://www.qbitai.com/2026/02/378286.html","date":"2026-02-10 07:18:25","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_c72c00fd.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"量子位","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":12,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_68451714","title":"阿里达摩院开源具身大脑基模：3B 激活参数性能超越 72B，转身就忘事的机器人有救了","link":"https://www.qbitai.com/2026/02/378236.html","date":"2026-02-10 03:19:14","oneSentenceSummary":"阿里达摩院开源 RynnBrain 具身大脑基础模型，通过 MoE 架构和时空记忆机制，显著提升了机器人在物理空间中的感知、推理与长程任务规划能力。","summary":"本文介绍了阿里达摩院最新开源的 RynnBrain 具身大脑基础模型系列（2B 到 30B）。该模型旨在解决具身机器人缺乏三维物理空间感知、容易遗忘历史状态的痛点。RynnBrain 是业界首个拥有时空记忆的具身大脑模型，在 20 项具身 Benchmark 中取得 16 个 SOTA。其核心技术亮点包括：采用 MoE 架构，实现 3B 激活参数性能超越 72B 稠密模型；自研 RynnScale 架构使训练速度提升 200%；基于 2000 万对高质量语料训练，增强了空间认知与 OCR 能力。达摩院倡导“大小脑分层架构”，并配套开源了评测基准 RynnBrain-Bench，旨在降低行业研发门槛，构建具身智能生态。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_68451714.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"量子位","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":17,"score":85},{"id":"RAW_cedf4ef1","title":"把电价当量化交易做！这家 AI 公司，一年帮数据中心“赚”出 1000 万","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNTY1MjE2OA==&mid=2247493323&idx=1&sn=eef073d7178259a645b49f3659c4ba69","date":"2026-02-09 11:03:00","oneSentenceSummary":"本文深度解析了达卯科技如何利用 AI 能源大模型，针对 AI 数据中心高波动用电特性，在电力现货交易市场中实现算电协同与成本优化。","summary":"文章探讨了在新能源占比提升和 AI 算力负载波动的双重挑战下，中国电力系统向市场化转型的背景。重点介绍了达卯科技的解决方案：通过全栈自研的能源大模型，将数据中心的服务器负载、储能、蓄冷等资源标准化为“能量块”序列，利用 AI 实时生成最优电力交易报价与调度方案。该模式在上海临港智算中心得到验证，实现年度电费降低 6.5%（约 1000 万元）。此外，文章还分析了其“低前端费+后端收益分成”的类基金商业模式，以及算电协同领域高达千亿级的市场潜力。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_cedf4ef1.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"乌鸦智能说","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":19,"score":85},{"id":"RAW_143cb1eb","title":"今日开源（2026-2-9）：美团 LongCat-Flash-Lite 开源，256k 长上下文+MoE 高效推理，嵌入优化超越等效基线","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247501588&idx=1&sn=9aade4d280c20d77f9840b0c2de6e9ca","date":"2026-02-09 10:31:00","oneSentenceSummary":"本文汇总了 2026 年 2 月初发布的多个前沿开源 AI 项目，重点介绍了美团 LongCat-Flash-Lite 长上下文模型及其他在世界模型、生物分子预测和 AI 编码评测领域的突破。","summary":"文章精选并简要介绍了六项最新的开源 AI 技术成果。核心项目包括美团开发的 LongCat-Flash-Lite，这是一个 68.5B 参数的 MoE 模型，支持 256k 长上下文并针对嵌入表进行了推理优化；Motus 潜在动作世界模型，采用混合变压器架构实现像素级动作提取；IntelliFold 2 在生物分子结构预测上超越了 AlphaFold3；UI-TARS Desktop 提供了原生 GUI Agent 体验；DreamZero 实现了动作与视频的同步预测；以及 ProjDevBench 这一针对 AI 编码 Agent 的端到端项目开发基准平台。这些项目反映了 AI 在长文本处理、具身智能和科学计算领域的快速演进。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_143cb1eb.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"机器之心SOTA模型","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":5,"score":86},{"id":"RAW_41ca7ce7","title":"清华刘知远团队论文：最小化结构改动，短文本到长文本丝滑升级 | ICLR 2026","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA5ODEzMjIyMA==&mid=2247731450&idx=2&sn=3894cd9c6cbb1819597afd469dbf1ce3","date":"2026-02-09 10:04:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_41ca7ce7.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"AI科技评论","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":20,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_48ab1cdc","title":"2026 年硅谷书单：18 位硅谷创始人共同推荐的 56 本书","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAxMDMxOTI2NA==&mid=2649104479&idx=1&sn=358e90989ecf328bc6bc47d22be5e315","date":"2026-02-09 09:56:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_48ab1cdc.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"十字路口Crossing","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":42,"score":84},{"id":"RAW_ed39a1a3","title":"快手用“对齐”技术，让广告推荐更懂你","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODkzMzMwMQ==&mid=2650450953&idx=1&sn=47ed7abd6a494f4735154972fa1cf2e7","date":"2026-02-09 07:25:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_ed39a1a3.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"AINLP","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":21,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_7d30dbd7","title":"警钟敲响！Hinton 最新万字演讲：怒怼乔姆斯基、定义“不朽计算”、揭示人类唯一生路","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg4NDQwNTI0OQ==&mid=2247588749&idx=1&sn=ba00f3e94e3cfa8387dca5401ee07ce5","date":"2026-02-09 04:01:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_7d30dbd7.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"AI科技大本营","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":42,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_b4495599","title":"世界是快的","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzNDQxOTU2MQ==&mid=2247512890&idx=1&sn=cd1fcfdc1581233000ced06131715007","date":"2026-02-09 03:55:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_b4495599.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"赛博禅心","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":18,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_94bf372a","title":"先解行为，再训 Agent：CMU 开源首份 Agentic Search 日志数据，把 Agent 拆开给你看","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2651016172&idx=3&sn=39404c16b766f404d8268a05ae66df30","date":"2026-02-09 01:16:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_94bf372a.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"机器之心","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":19,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_12a5d7d1","title":"英伟达世界模型再进化，一个模型驱动所有机器人！机器人的 GPT 时刻真正到来","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2651016172&idx=2&sn=faf9feb8f73897e4396039ad1f21bde3","date":"2026-02-09 01:16:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_12a5d7d1.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"机器之心","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":11,"score":82},{"id":"RAW_ef793c6a","title":"童年的滚球兽「走进」现实？华为天才少年创业，全球首个虚实融合的实时交互视频模型来了","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2651016172&idx=1&sn=ba86881c1213117489b6b5d8ddfa2778","date":"2026-02-09 01:16:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_ef793c6a.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"机器之心","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":17,"score":82},{"id":"RAW_eb9c50c3","title":"前 Codex 大神倒戈实锤！吹爆 Claude Code：编程提速 5 倍，点破 OpenAl 死穴在上下文","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MDE0Mjc4MA==&mid=2651275013&idx=1&sn=676ba2f122e957a2595dea61981f46e9","date":"2026-02-10 06:05:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_eb9c50c3.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ 中文","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":62,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_9c115a8b","title":"别再让语音机器人“答非所问”：AI Force 任务型语音对话技术总结","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIzOTU0NTQ0MA==&mid=2247558288&idx=1&sn=1e34f7eae3421e09e8f2f78baeb5f066","date":"2026-02-10 00:32:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_9c115a8b.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"阿里云开发者","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":29,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_0df11db4","title":"实现 GPU 大幅降本！顺丰科技基于自研的算力资源管理与调度实践","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzMjYzNjkzNw==&mid=2247634464&idx=1&sn=76edbd50ff2bb5660711db5e4b67c42c","date":"2026-02-09 23:15:00","oneSentenceSummary":"顺丰科技自研的 EffectiveGPU 方案通过 CUDA 劫持技术实现了 GPU 的细粒度切分、算力与显存双维度超分，并结合 Volcano 调度器显著提升了资源利用率与降本效果。","summary":"本文详细介绍了顺丰科技为解决传统 GPU 独占模式导致的资源浪费问题，自研的 EffectiveGPU (EGPU) 资源管理方案。该方案采用 CUDA 劫持技术，在不侵入业务的前提下实现了显存和算力的精准切分与隔离。EGPU 核心组件包括劫持内核、设备插件、自定义调度器及 Webhook，支持强/弱算力限制及高低优先级调度。通过与 Volcano 深度集成，实现了基于 GPU 型号的精准调度和租户资源管控。最后，文章通过训推一体、切分共享、显存超分三个实战案例，展示了该方案在实际生产环境中的显著降本成效。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_0df11db4.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"dbaplus社群","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":31,"score":86},{"id":"RAW_7b4faaf5","title":"为什么代码需求是无限的：AI 如何创造更多开发者岗位","link":"https://stackoverflow.blog/2026/02/09/why-demand-for-code-is-infinite-how-ai-creates-more-developer-jobs/","date":"2026-02-09 17:00:00","oneSentenceSummary":"本文认为 AI 是一场变革性的平台转型，它非但不会取代开发者，反而会通过赋能人类解决日益复杂的问题，触发对代码的无限需求。","summary":"文章反驳了 AI 将消除软件工程岗位的观点，将 AI 视为类似于互联网、移动端和云计算的重大平台转型。文章指出，历史上每一个技术抽象层最终都增加了对专业人才的需求。通过降低准入门槛和处理常规编码任务，AI 让开发者能够专注于由无限人类想象力驱动的高阶问题。文中概述了硬件、模型、基础设施和应用层机会的“寒武纪大爆发”，同时识别了如 AI 编排师和人机协作架构师等新兴角色。结论是，开发的未来在于人类判断力与 AI 效率相结合的乘数效应。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_7b4faaf5.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"Stack Overflow Blog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":9,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_832433c3","title":"构建 Prometheus：后端聚合如何实现吉瓦级 AI 集群","link":"https://engineering.fb.com/2026/02/09/data-center-engineering/building-prometheus-how-backend-aggregation-enables-gigawatt-scale-ai-clusters/","date":"2026-02-09 16:48:38","oneSentenceSummary":"Meta 的后端聚合 (BAG) 架构通过提供中心化、高容量的以太网超级主干，连接区域数据中心和多种网络架构，从而实现了吉瓦级 AI 集群。","summary":"本文详细介绍了 Meta 的 1 吉瓦 AI 集群 Prometheus 的架构，重点阐述了后端聚合 (BAG) 的关键作用。BAG 作为一个中心化的以太网超级主干层，连接了多个数据中心和区域，支持数万个 GPU。它利用 Jericho3 ASIC 等模块化硬件，桥接了不同的架构技术，特别是解耦调度架构 (DSF) 和非调度架构 (NSF)。该设计强调拍比特 (petabit) 级的带宽、弹性拓扑（平面与分散）以及通过 eBGP/UCMP 实现的高级路由。一个关键的技术亮点是使用深缓存 (deep-buffer) 交换机来管理长距离跨建筑连接的延迟和拥塞，确保大规模 AI 工作负载的无损性能。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_832433c3.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"Engineering at Meta","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":4,"score":86},{"id":"RAW_0fd403e0","title":"你是否遗漏了 Data Frame？Java 中 Data Frame 的力量","link":"https://www.infoq.com/presentations/data-frames-java/?utm_campaign=infoq_content&utm_source=infoq&utm_medium=feed&utm_term=global","date":"2026-02-09 15:02:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_0fd403e0.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":23,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_89098486","title":"Vercel 如何构建针对编程智能体的 AEO 追踪系统","link":"https://vercel.com/blog/how-we-built-aeo-tracking-for-coding-agents","date":"2026-02-09 13:00:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_89098486.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"Vercel News","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":9,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_a62dcd11","title":"任何人都能构建智能体，但运行它们需要一个平台 - Vercel","link":"https://vercel.com/blog/anyone-can-build-agents-but-it-takes-a-platform-to-run-them","date":"2026-02-09 13:00:00","oneSentenceSummary":"Vercel 认为，虽然 AI 降低了智能体原型设计的门槛，但真正的竞争优势在于能够管理生产级安全、可靠性和成本的强大平台。","summary":"本文探讨了 AI 开发格局的变化，指出虽然得益于 LLM，构建智能体已变得非常简单，但大规模运行它们仍然是一个复杂的工程挑战。文章引入了“内部 AI 技术栈”的概念，这是从“氛围感编程”迈向可靠生产环境的必要条件。Vercel 展示了其智能体编排平台，并以其内部数据智能体 d0 作为主要案例研究。文章详细介绍了特定的基础设施原语——包括用于代码执行的安全沙箱、用于扩展不可预测工作负载的 Fluid Compute、用于模型管理的 AI Gateway 以及用于错误恢复的持久工作流——如何构成了现代智能体架构的基础。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_a62dcd11.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"Vercel News","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":6,"score":90},{"id":"RAW_16225284","title":"在资源受限的环境中构建 LLM：实战视角","link":"https://www.infoq.com/articles/building-llms-resource-constrained-environments/?utm_campaign=infoq_content&utm_source=infoq&utm_medium=feed&utm_term=global","date":"2026-02-09 11:31:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_16225284.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":12,"score":85},{"id":"RAW_d05aef0d","title":"[视频播客] 与 Madelyn Olson 探讨 Valkey 的改进","link":"https://www.infoq.com/podcasts/valkey-performance-improvements/?utm_campaign=infoq_content&utm_source=infoq&utm_medium=feed&utm_term=global","date":"2026-02-09 11:00:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_d05aef0d.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":30,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_f20403ee","title":"Flink ClickHouse Sink：生产级高可用写入方案｜得物技术","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkxNTE3ODU0NA==&mid=2247542990&idx=1&sn=95c80d04da0238e8e16312f48c1a1f5f","date":"2026-02-09 10:36:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_f20403ee.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"得物技术","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":35,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_d6825afe","title":"OpenSpec：面向 AI 编程的规范驱动开发框架","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg4MTYwMzY1Mw==&mid=2247517997&idx=1&sn=ba0a8c9bf05522b81f2b383aa2db9ac9","date":"2026-02-09 10:30:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_d6825afe.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"奇舞精选","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":87,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_fdedec8b","title":"AI 产品用户留存仅三个月周期？对话王咏刚：“不和 AI 协作过项目，你就不是合格程序员” | 万有引力","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzMDY1NDgyOQ==&mid=2247828079&idx=1&sn=93a911194a4e1f17a61661025462ecb9","date":"2026-02-09 10:29:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_fdedec8b.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"CSDN","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":73,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_c4f8c7e7","title":"警钟敲响！Hinton 最新万字演讲：怒怼乔姆斯基、定义“不朽计算”、揭示人类唯一生路","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzMDY1NDgyOQ==&mid=2247828079&idx=2&sn=774af098fd47c021bcfe501132287f3a","date":"2026-02-09 10:29:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_c4f8c7e7.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"CSDN","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":42,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_3b94f1fc","title":"百度沧海·存储 Mantle 系统架构演进之路，SOSP'25 论文背后的故事","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg5MjU0NTI5OQ==&mid=2247606328&idx=1&sn=d5787876fa3110535cca564c2c839e4f","date":"2026-02-09 10:01:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_3b94f1fc.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"百度Geek说","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":62,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_8e27286a","title":"设计模式 Trustworthy Generation：提升 RAG 信赖度","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAxNDEwNjk5OQ==&mid=2650542871&idx=1&sn=30f0fa05c0a2129017f6f3f19812a491","date":"2026-02-09 09:17:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_8e27286a.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"大淘宝技术","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":19,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_f72ad988","title":"当 OpenClaw 内置 LanceDB：为个人 AI 智能体打造超强长期记忆","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MzYzMjE0MQ==&mid=2247518417&idx=1&sn=27cf117f0487cff41839aaaaf4de2545","date":"2026-02-09 06:03:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_f72ad988.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"字节跳动技术团队","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":20,"score":85},{"id":"RAW_7867d70b","title":"AI 周刊 #070 - Codex 桌面应用发布、GPT-5.3-Codex & Claude Opus 4.6 发布","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIzOTkwMjM0OQ==&mid=2247546036&idx=1&sn=0116fe4cc852abe28fff6cfbc1f9c49a","date":"2026-02-09 02:00:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_7867d70b.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"印记中文","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":11,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_bdde6ae5","title":"借助 AI Coding 快速打造 AI Agent 系统","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIzOTU0NTQ0MA==&mid=2247558316&idx=1&sn=6a53c77fe9bdb8b35a1d513897c4a472","date":"2026-02-09 00:31:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_bdde6ae5.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"阿里云开发者","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":37,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_15cd3e76","title":"面对  OpenClaw，苹果选择刀背藏身","link":"https://www.ifanr.com/1654588?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=","date":"2026-02-10 09:36:09","oneSentenceSummary":"本文深度解析了苹果在 AI Agent 浪潮中的「刀背藏身」策略：通过提供高性能硬件（Mac Mini）支持开源 Agent 运行，既规避了直接挑战巨头条款的法律风险，又通过硬件溢价和生态隔离实现了商业利益最大化。","summary":"文章探讨了 2026 年（设定背景）OpenClaw 等 AI Agent 意外带火 Mac Mini 的现象，并深入分析了苹果为何不亲自下场做「超级 Siri」。核心逻辑在于：若苹果官方内置自动化 Agent，将直接违反 Meta、LinkedIn 等平台的反自动化条款，面临巨大的法律诉讼风险。相反，苹果选择将 macOS 维持为「通用计算机」属性，让用户在本地运行开源代码，从而实现风险隔离。同时，苹果利用统一内存架构和 MLX 框架，将 Mac 打造为运行大模型的最优性价比硬件。这种策略延续了苹果在 ATT 时代「以隐私之名行打击竞争对手之实」的作风，既收割了硬件利润，又在战略上通过本地 AI 瓦解了依赖广告和注意力的旧互联网商业模式。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_15cd3e76.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"爱范儿","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":16,"score":85},{"id":"RAW_796ba472","title":"2026-02-10 Hacker News Top Stories #","link":"https://supertechfans.com/cn/post/2026-02-10-HackerNews/","date":"2026-02-10 09:00:56","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_796ba472.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"SuperTechFans","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":66,"score":86},{"id":"RAW_ae00ea60","title":"程前访谈陈森雁：我裁掉了 20 人的拍摄团队，一年白捡 100 万","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIxNTAzNzU0Ng==&mid=2654903209&idx=2&sn=e4f0836c0a169cb7e61a4da47a576130","date":"2026-02-09 13:31:00","oneSentenceSummary":"广州服装厂老板陈森雁分享如何利用 ComfyUI 等 AI 工具链替代 20 人拍摄团队，实现单张模特图 5 毛钱成本、15 秒出图的工业化降本增效方案。","summary":"本文是针对 1688 男装头部商家陈森雁的深度访谈。文章详细阐述了服装电商如何利用 AI 技术解决传统拍摄中成本高（模特、影棚、修图）、周期长（10-15 天）以及测款不确定性等痛点。陈森雁展示了由专属 AI 模型、ComfyUI 自动化工作流、OneTing AI 算力平台及作图软件构成的“四件套”工具链，实现了虚拟模特的高清、多姿态、跨场景生成。此外，文章还介绍了如何结合电商平台 AI 工具进行选品洞察、店铺诊断和精准客户运营，将 AI 从单点提效扩展至全链路智能升级。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_ae00ea60.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"笔记侠","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":18,"score":85},{"id":"RAW_5585a96a","title":"即梦 Seedance2.0 视频模型\"王者归来\"之后 | 最新突发: 模型太强以至禁止了真人人脸支持...","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIxODUzNTg2MA==&mid=2247489943&idx=1&sn=b77584f14c2c449d78b6c1e169cc67b1","date":"2026-02-09 10:29:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_5585a96a.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"Web3天空之城","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":13,"score":82},{"id":"RAW_96a3c531","title":"2026-02-09 Hacker News Top Stories #","link":"https://supertechfans.com/cn/post/2026-02-09-HackerNews/","date":"2026-02-09 08:57:18","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_96a3c531.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"SuperTechFans","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":67,"sco